{"tid":1826562,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"革命先賢既智慧，大家睇睇佢","createTime":"2020-01-16T08:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T08:45:36.000Z","uid":296361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d69152ad1621ce7fb39597ad4a5711298ce04ad","tid":1826562,"uid":296361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"革命之事譬如煮飯。煮飯之要具有二：一曰釜，一曰薪。釜之為德，在一恒字。水不能蝕，火不能熔，水火交煎，皆能忍受。此正如我革命黨人，百折不撓，再接再厲。薪之為德，在一烈字。炬火熊熊，光焰萬丈，顧體質雖毀，借其餘熱，可以煮飯。此正如我革命黨人，一往獨前，捨生取義"},{"pid":"f00fc9c7612783c189c83a904d57ac62335fb1e2","tid":1826562,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:44:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=83107a3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"06733fd090a98c81618724754e50723edf4447de","tid":1826562,"uid":296361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"所以勇武同和理非，其實缺一不可，<br />\n要有剛勇如烈火，也要有人持之以恆，百折不撓，不停給壓力"}]}